UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 222
1 the department is greater by twenty-five percent (25%) or more than the
2 amount returned by the owner, the excess shall be assessed by the
3 department within six (6) years from the date the return was filed.
4 (11) Any owner who violates this section shall be subject to the uniform civil penalties
5 imposed pursuant to KRS 131.180 and interest at the tax interest rate as defined
6 in KRS 131.183.
